title: Medium Energy Neutral Atom (MENA) H Images, Key Parameters, IMAGE - Dr. Craig Pollock (SwRI)

info.x_cadence_note: Counts based on variable 'Epoch' in https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/sp_phys/data/image/mena/mena_k0/2000/im_k0_mena_20000404_v01.cdf. The most common cadence, 119998 [ms] = PT1M59.998S, occurred for 3.0488% of the 10 timesteps.
